# Differential state management

## Description

Streaming state updates and garbage collection.

## Implementation

```rust
pub struct Differentialstatemanagement {
    state: StreamingState,
    changes: Vec<Change>,
}

impl Differentialstatemanagement {
    pub fn process_changes(&mut self, input: Vec<Change>) -> Vec<Change> {
        // Incremental processing
        let mut output = Vec::new();
        for change in input {
            output.extend(self.apply_change(change));
        }
        output
    }
}
```

## Cost Model

- Update cost: O(changes) not O(data)
- 100-1000x faster than recomputation
- State size: O(active_data)

## References

1. McSherry et al., "Differential Dataflow", CIDR 2013
2. Materialize documentation
